lead_paragraph: Ariya Jutanugarn was flirting with another Sunday meltdown, her six-stroke lead down to one after a double bogey on the par-4 13th at tree-lined Woburn.

headline.print_headline: Thailand's Ariya Jutanugarn Wins Women's British Open
